OL,3,CPair who rescued neighbour being
OL,4,Cstabbed by intruder in her home
OL,5,Creceive award
OL,7,FTwo women from Lydney have received a
OL,8,Fnational police bravery award for
OL,9,Fconfronting an intruder who stabbed
OL,10,Ftheir neighbour four times.
OL,12,FLizzie Powell, 55, and Marion Balaam,
OL,13,F65, came to the aid of off-duty police
OL,14,Fofficer Hannah Conroy on 28 May 2023
OL,15,Fwhen they heard screams coming from
OL,16,Fher house.
