OL,4,Cstabbed by intruder in her home
OL,5,Creceive award
OL,7,FHannah was woken by banging downstairs
OL,8,Fin her terraced house at around 4am
OL,9,Fand walked downstairs to find Joanna
OL,10,FMammatt, 41, armed with a large
OL,11,Fkitchen knife.
OL,13,FHannah screamed for help and was
OL,14,Fstabbed four times.
OL,16,FNext door, Lizzie heard her cries and
OL,17,Fcalled the emergency services before
OL,18,Frunning to Hannah's front door.
