OL,4,Cstabbed by intruder in her home
OL,5,Creceive award
OL,7,FLizzie said: "I banged on the door and
OL,8,Fshouted 'Police!' I'm not sure why I
OL,9,Fdid that.
OL,11,F"I could hear them fighting inside.
OL,12,FThe door opened and Hannah was covered
OL,13,Fin blood and she just said 'she
OL,14,Fstabbed me'.
OL,16,F"The instant reaction was to grab
OL,17,FJoanna by the hair and pull her
OL,18,Foutside away from Hannah. Hannah then
OL,19,Fthrew her handcuffs to me to try and
OL,20,Fcontain her.
