OL,5,Creceive award
OL,7,F"I was like: I have no idea what to do
OL,8,Fwith these!"
OL,10,FMarion, who lives across the street,
OL,11,Fwas also woken by the banging and
OL,12,Fscreams.
OL,14,FShe arrived in her dressing gown to
OL,15,Ffind Lizzie on the floor with Joanna.
OL,17,FMarion said: "I went into Hannah's
OL,18,Fhouse and there was blood everywhere.
OL,19,FI could see she had a gaping wound. I
OL,20,Fgot her to sit down on the sofa and
OL,21,Fwent to put pressure on the wound."
