OL,7,FHannah was taken to hospital shortly
OL,8,Fafter and underwent two surgeries. It
OL,9,Ftook her six months to recover from
OL,10,Fher injuries.
OL,12,FShe said although they "play it down",
OL,13,Fher neighbours saved her life.
OL,15,F"They're two of the strongest, most
OL,16,Fwarrior women I know, and my lifelong
OL,17,Ffriends now," Hannah said.
OL,19,F"I'm very, very lucky."
