OL,7,FThe pair say they're "incredibly
OL,8,Fproud" of their actions but insist
OL,9,Fthey were only doing what anyone else
OL,10,Fwould have done.
OL,12,FJoanna Mammatt was found not guilty of
OL,13,Fattempted murder by reason of insanity
OL,14,Fin August 2024 and remains under the
OL,15,Fjurisdiction of a mental health team.
